text: Neustadt an der Waldnaab (Bavarian: Neistodt an da Woidnaab) is a municipality in Bavaria, Germany, and capital of the district Neustadt an der Waldnaab. == Twin towns and cities == Neustadt an der Waldnaab has one sister city: * Hays, Kansas, USA ==References== Category:Neustadt an der Waldnaab (district)
title: Neustadt an der Waldnaab
